_sText:
Hi guys. I was thinking of a Working injured guy, Which if you damage him, he dies.
And I made this Prefab! I made this to show you how to make a Injured Person to die by taking damage! (Without any mods and NPCs!)
I'll be glad if people make/use these Prefabs in their CS Source map and increase the realisticity of their maps xd

Extract the Prefab anywhere you wish and use Valve Hammer Editor to open the .vmf!
